name: cmsAuth
body:
### Welcome to cmsAuth.
cmsAuth is a python-django web application which serves as a extension for [Contest Management System](http://cms-dev.github.io/). 


### Authors and Contributors
By now I'm the only author (@slosimon). If you want to use the tool, you are the most welcome to help improving this tool. In Slovenia, we are using CMS as a training system for IOI and other olympiads in informatics so we had to improve the tool. 

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Check out my [documentation](http://cmsauth.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) or [contact support](mailto:weiss.simon.1995@gmail.com) and Iâ€™ll help you sort it out.
